data.description: Welcome to 136 Beth Dr, Felton, CA 95018, a delightful 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom residence spanning 1,226 sqft. Embraced by the beauty of towering redwood trees, this home provides a special riverside ambiance just moments from your doorstep. Revel in the tranquility of the outdoors and the crisp air within the expansive backyard. Recent enhancements have elevated the interior with new carpeting, fresh paint, and contemporary light fixtures. Inside, discover a harmonious mix of hardwood and carpeted floors, creating an inviting atmosphere. With a touch of extra effort, this serene sanctuary holds tremendous potential. The elongated driveway ensures ample parking convenience. Seize the opportunity to transform this peaceful retreat into your new home!
